headline: Primerica Reloads Buyback Canon With a Fresh $475M Program
summary: PRI boosts shareholder returns with a new $475M buyback as strong Term Life momentum and solid liquidity support continued capital generation.

headline: The Hartford’s CEO Convenes Leader Group To Explore Vision For City Of Hartford’s Future
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., November 20, 2025--The Hartford’s Chairman and CEO Christopher Swift has convened a group of corporate and community leaders in Greater Hartford to explore the development of a unifying vision for the City of Hartford.
